When nineteen-year-old huntress Feyre kills a wolf in the woods, a beast-like creature arrives to demand retribution for it. But an ancient, wicked shadow grows over the faerie lands, and Feyre must find a way to stop itâ€¦ or doom Tamlinâ€”and his worldâ€”forever.

Perfect for fans of Kristin Cashore and George R. R. Martin, this first book in a sexy and action-packed new series is impossible to put down
